---
// EngagementFlow component - displays 4-step engagement process
---

<section class="engagement-flow">
    <div class="container">
        <div class="flow-content">
            <h2 class="heading-lg">Typical Engagement Model</h2>
            <p class="tagline">Engagements are intentionally focused to drive outcomes.</p>

            <div class="flow-steps">
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-icon-container">
                        <svg class="step-icon" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M32 12 L52 52 L12 52 Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="5.5" stroke-linejoin="miter" />
                            <text x="32" y="40" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle" class="step-number">1</text>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="step-label">Align</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="step-text">Introductory discussion to clarify objectives, decision context, and constraints</p>
                    <div class="step-divider"></div>
                    <p class="step-detail">Confidential, no-commitment conversation. We assess fit, understand your timeline, and identify the highest-leverage questions to answer first. Typical duration: 30 to 60 minutes.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-icon-container">
                        <svg class="step-icon" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M32 12 L52 52 L12 52 Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="5.5" stroke-linejoin="miter" />
                            <text x="32" y="40" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle" class="step-number">2</text>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="step-label">Define</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="step-text">Focused scope aligned to decision-critical priorities</p>
                    <div class="step-divider"></div>
                    <p class="step-detail">We design a work plan targeting your specific risk areas, whether that's a 2-week diligence sprint or a 90-day remediation roadmap. No boilerplate. Every deliverable maps to a decision you need to make.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-icon-container">
                        <svg class="step-icon" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M32 12 L52 52 L12 52 Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="5.5" stroke-linejoin="miter" />
                            <text x="32" y="40" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle" class="step-number">3</text>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="step-label">Deliver</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="step-text">Clear findings, prioritized recommendations, and implementation-ready path forward</p>
                    <div class="step-divider"></div>
                    <p class="step-detail">Executive-ready outputs with quantified risk, concrete remediation steps, and priority-ranked recommendations. Every finding includes severity, business impact, and a clear next action.</p>
                </div>
                <div class="step">
                    <div class="step-icon-container">
                        <svg class="step-icon" viewBox="0 0 64 64" fill="none" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg">
                            <path d="M32 12 L52 52 L12 52 Z" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="5.5" stroke-linejoin="miter" />
                            <text x="32" y="40" text-anchor="middle" dominant-baseline="middle" class="step-number">4</text>
                        </svg>
                        <span class="step-label">Guide</span>
                    </div>
                    <p class="step-text">Optional ongoing advisory or execution support</p>
                    <div class="step-divider"></div>
                    <p class="step-detail">Fractional engagement model: weekly or monthly cadence scaled to your needs. Board prep, architecture reviews, vendor evaluations, or hands-on execution alongside your team. Disengage anytime.</p>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<style>
    .engagement-flow {
        padding: var(--spacing-3xl) 0;
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(245, 245, 245, 0) 0%, var(--bg-light-alt) 15%, var(--bg-light-alt) 85%, rgba(245, 245, 245, 0) 100%);
        position: relative;
    }

    .flow-content {
        max-width: 1100px;
        margin: 0 auto;
    }

    .heading-lg {
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
        text-align: center;
    }

    .tagline {
        text-align: center;
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        color: var(--text-light-secondary);
        line-height: 1.7;
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-2xl);
        max-width: 800px;
        margin-left: auto;
        margin-right: auto;
    }

    .flow-steps {
        display: grid;
        grid-template-columns: repeat(4, 1fr);
        gap: var(--spacing-lg);
    }

    .step {
        padding: var(--spacing-xl);
        background: var(--bg-light-primary);
        border: 1px solid var(--border-light);
        border-radius: 8px;
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        text-align: center;
        transition: all 0.3s ease;
    }

    .step:hover {
        border-color: var(--color-primary);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.1);
        transform: translateY(-2px);
    }

    .step-icon-container {
        display: flex;
        flex-direction: column;
        align-items: center;
        gap: var(--spacing-sm);
        margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
    }

    .step-icon {
        width: 5.25rem;
        height: 5.25rem;
        flex-shrink: 0;
        color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    .step-number {
        font-size: 1.28rem;
        font-weight: 700;
        fill: var(--text-light-primary);
    }

    .step-label {
        font-size: 0.875rem;
        font-weight: 600;
        color: var(--text-light-secondary);
        text-transform: uppercase;
        letter-spacing: 0.05em;
    }

    .step-text {
        font-size: var(--text-base);
        color: var(--text-light-primary);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
    }

    .step-divider {
        width: 2rem;
        height: 2px;
        border: none;
        background: var(--color-primary);
        opacity: 0.4;
        margin: var(--spacing-lg) 0;
    }

    .step-detail {
        font-size: var(--text-small);
        color: var(--text-light-muted);
        line-height: 1.6;
        margin: 0;
    }

    /* Dark theme support */
    :global(html.dark-theme) .engagement-flow {
        background: linear-gradient(180deg, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0) 0%, var(--bg-dark) 15%, var(--bg-dark) 85%, rgba(10, 10, 10, 0) 100%);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .step {
        background: var(--bg-dark-alt);
        border-color: var(--border-dark);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .step:hover {
        border-color: var(--color-primary);
        box-shadow: 0 4px 12px rgba(5, 205, 153, 0.15);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .step-text {
        color: var(--text-dark-primary);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .step-detail {
        color: var(--text-dark-muted);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .step-icon {
        color: var(--color-primary);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .step-number {
        fill: var(--text-dark-primary);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .tagline {
        color: var(--text-dark-secondary);
    }

    :global(html.dark-theme) .step-label {
        color: var(--text-dark-secondary);
    }

    /* Responsive design */
    @media (max-width: 1024px) {
        .flow-steps {
            grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);
            gap: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .step {
            padding: var(--spacing-lg);
        }

        .step-icon {
            width: 4.72rem;
            height: 4.72rem;
        }

        .step-number {
            font-size: 1.18rem;
        }

        .step-label {
            font-size: 0.8rem;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 768px) {
        .engagement-flow {
            padding: var(--spacing-2xl) 0;
        }

        .flow-steps {
            grid-template-columns: 1fr;
            gap: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .heading-lg {
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .tagline {
            font-size: var(--text-small);
            margin-bottom: var(--spacing-lg);
        }

        .step {
            padding: var(--spacing-lg);
        }

        .step-icon {
            width: 4.2rem;
            height: 4.2rem;
        }

        .step-number {
            font-size: 1.02rem;
        }

        .step-label {
            font-size: 0.75rem;
        }

        .step-text {
            font-size: var(--text-small);
        }

        .step-detail {
            font-size: var(--text-tiny);
        }

        .step-divider {
            margin: var(--spacing-md) 0;
        }
    }

    @media (max-width: 480px) {
        .engagement-flow {
            padding: var(--spacing-xl) 0;
        }

        .step {
            padding: var(--spacing-md);
        }

        .step-text {
            font-size: var(--text-small);
            line-height: 1.5;
        }
    }
</style>
